Our client Paul is opening his own Crossfit gym in Signal Hill. Crossfit is a relatively new cultural phenomena that makes fitness a sport. It uses a combination of aerobic exercise and weightlifting to help people become more fit. Crossfit gyms across the country have utilized interactive websites to provide information to customers and show them what Crossfit is all about.

Paul has requested a content management system-based website to help promote the opening of his new gym in early February. He would like a way to manage the content on their website to keep their gym members up-to-date on new promotions and fitness related news. The site will also be invaluable to the success of the gym as it will become a very effective way to draw in customers.
